.SS Remote API tokens
.sp
When Wiswa configures the remote (\fBwiswa\fP without \fB\-\-skip\-remote\fP), it calls the GitHub or
GitLab API using a \fBpersonal access token\fP\&. Tokens are read from the environment when supported,
or from the system keyring. Service names include the \fBrepository hostname\fP so different hosts
(for example GitHub.com, GitHub Enterprise, or self\-managed GitLab) keep separate credentials.
.sp
Keyring entries use the usual \fBservice name\fP and \fBusername\fP fields. The \fBusername\fP is
normally your OS login name (\fBwhoami\fP).
.SS GitHub
.INDENT 0.0
.IP 1. 3
Service \fBwiswa\-github:<hostname>\fP, username your OS user. The hostname is taken from
\fBrepository_uri\fP (for example \fBgithub.com\fP for \fBhttps://github.com/org/repo\fP).
.UNINDENT
.sp
Example (hostname \fBgithub.com\fP, OS user \fBalice\fP):
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
python \-m keyring set \(aqwiswa\-github:github.com\(aq alice
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS GitLab
.INDENT 0.0
.IP 1. 3
\fBEnvironment:\fP \fBGITLAB_TOKEN\fP (if set, used first).
.IP 2. 3
\fBPreferred:\fP service \fBwiswa\-gitlab:<hostname>\fP, username your OS user (for example
\fBwiswa\-gitlab:gitlab.com\fP).
.IP 3. 3
The same service with \fBusername\fP equal to the hostname is also checked.
.UNINDENT
.sp
Example for \fBgitlab.com\fP:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
export GITLAB_TOKEN=\(aqglpat\-...\(aq

python \-m keyring set \(aqwiswa\-gitlab:gitlab.com\(aq \(dq$(whoami)\(dq
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS MCP Server
.sp
Wiswa includes an MCP server (\fBwiswa\-mcp\fP) that exposes settings discovery tools for AI
assistants.
.SS Claude Code
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
claude mcp add wiswa\-mcp \-\- wiswa\-mcp
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS Cursor
.sp
Add to \fB\&.cursor/mcp.json\fP:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
{
  \(dqmcpServers\(dq: {
    \(dqwiswa\-mcp\(dq: {
      \(dqcommand\(dq: \(dqwiswa\-mcp\(dq
    }
  }
}
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS GitHub Copilot CLI
.sp
Add to \fB\&.github/copilot/mcp.json\fP:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
{
  \(dqmcpServers\(dq: {
    \(dqwiswa\-mcp\(dq: {
      \(dqcommand\(dq: \(dqwiswa\-mcp\(dq
    }
  }
}
.EE
